- `GET /api/v1/locations` - Get library locations
- `GET /api/v1/rooms` - Get all rooms
- `GET /api/v1/rooms/{id}` - Get room details
- `GET /api/v1/rooms/{id}/availability?date=YYYY-MM-DD` - Get room availability
- `GET /api/v1/bookings?date=YYYY-MM-DD` - Get existing bookings
- `POST /api/v1/bookings` - Create new booking
- `DELETE /api/v1/bookings/{id}` - Cancel booking